{"id":139,"ayahs":[{"number":91,"arabic":"وَمَا قَدَرُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ حَقَّ قَدْرِهِۦٓ إِذْ قَالُوا۟ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ بَشَرٍۢ مِّن شَىْءٍۢ ۗ قُلْ مَنْ أَنزَلَ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ ٱلَّذِى جَآءَ بِهِۦ مُوسَىٰ نُورًۭا وَهُدًۭى لِّلنَّاسِ ۖ تَجْعَلُونَهُۥ قَرَاطِيسَ تُبْدُونَهَا وَتُخْفُونَ كَثِيرًۭا ۖ وَعُلِّمْتُم مَّا لَمْ تَعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنتُمْ وَلَآ ءَابَآؤُكُمْ ۖ قُلِ ٱللَّهُ ۖ ثُمَّ ذَرْهُمْ فِى خَوْضِهِمْ يَلْعَبُونَ","translation":"For, no true understanding of God have they when they say, \"Never has God revealed anything unto man.\" Say: \"Who has bestowed from on high the divine writ which Moses brought unto men as a light and a guidance, [and] which you treat as [mere] leaves of paper, making a show of them the while you conceal [so] much - although you have been taught [by it] what neither you nor your forefathers had ever known?\" Say: \"God [has revealed that divine writ]!\" - and then leave them to play at their vain talk.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/880.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":68266,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68267,"position":2,"arabic":"قَدَرُوا۟","translation":"তারা মর্যাদা দিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68268,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌কে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68269,"position":4,"arabic":"حَقَّ","translation":"যথাযথ","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68270,"position":5,"arabic":"قَدْرِهِۦٓ","translation":"মর্যাদা তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68271,"position":6,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68272,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68273,"position":8,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68274,"position":9,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"\"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68275,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68276,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68277,"position":12,"arabic":"بَشَرٍۢ","translation":"কোনো মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68278,"position":13,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68279,"position":14,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ ۗ","translation":"কিছুই (অর্থাৎ কিতাব)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68281,"position":15,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68282,"position":16,"arabic":"مَنْ","translation":"\"কে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68283,"position":17,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68284,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68285,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68286,"position":20,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"এসেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68287,"position":21,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"নিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68288,"position":22,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰ","translation":"মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68289,"position":23,"arabic":"نُورًۭا","translation":"আলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68290,"position":24,"arabic":"وَهُدًۭى","translation":"ও পথ নির্দেশস্বরূ