"","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68310,"position":40,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68311,"position":41,"arabic":"ذَرْهُمْ","translation":"ছেড়ে দাও তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_046.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68312,"position":42,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_047.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68313,"position":43,"arabic":"خَوْضِهِمْ","translation":"অর্থহীন আলোচনার তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_048.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68314,"position":44,"arabic":"يَلْعَبُونَ","translation":"তারা খেলতে থাকুক","audioUrl":"wbw/006_091_049.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68315,"position":45,"arabic":"٩١","translation":"(৯১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":92,"arabic":"وَهَٰذَا كِتَٰبٌ أَنزَلْنَٰهُ مُبَارَكٌۭ مُّصَدِّقُ ٱلَّذِى بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ وَلِتُنذِرَ أُمَّ ٱلْقُرَىٰ وَمَنْ حَوْلَهَا ۚ وَٱلَّذِينَ يُؤْمِنُونَ بِٱلْءَاخِرَةِ يُؤْمِنُونَ بِهِۦ ۖ وَهُمْ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمْ يُحَافِظُونَ","translation":"And this, too, is a divine writ which We have bestowed from on high - blessed, confirming the truth of whatever there still remains [of earlier revelations] -and [this] in order that thou mayest warn the foremost of all cities and all who dwell around it. And those who believe in the life to come do believe in this [warning]; and it is they who are ever-mindful of their prayers.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/881.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":68622,"position":1,"arabic":"وَهَـٰذَا","translation":"এবং এই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68623,"position":2,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبٌ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68624,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ","translation":"আমরা অবতীর্ণ করেছি তা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68625,"position":4,"arabic":"مُبَارَكٌۭ","translation":"কল্যাণময়","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68626,"position":5,"arabic":"مُّصَدِّقُ","translation":"সত্যায়নকারী (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68627,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68628,"position":7,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68629,"position":8,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"হাতের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68630,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلِتُنذِرَ","translation":"এবং যেন তুমি সতর্ক করো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68631,"position":10,"arabic":"أُمَّ","translation":"মা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68632,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرَىٰ","translation":"জনপদসমূহের (অর্থাৎ মক্কার লোকদেরকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68633,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"ও যারা (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68634,"position":13,"arabic":"حَوْلَهَا ۚ","translation":"চারপাশে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68636,"position":14,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"এবং যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68637,"position":15,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68638,"position":16,"arabic":"بِٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"উপর আখিরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68639,"position":17,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"তারা ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68640,"position":18,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۖ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68642,"position":19,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","translation":"এবং তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68643,"position":20,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68644,"position":21,"arabic":"صَلَاتِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের সালাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68645,"position":22,"arabic":"يُحَافِظُونَ","translation":"রক্ষা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_092_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":68646,"position":23,"arabic":"٩٢","translation":"(৯২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":93,"arabic":"وَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ مِمَّنِ ٱفْتَرَىٰ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ كَذِبًا أَوْ قَالَ أُوحِىَ إِلَىَّ وَلَمْ يُوحَ إِلَيْهِ شَىْءٌۭ وَمَن قَالَ سَأُنزِلُ مِثْلَ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ ۗ وَلَوْ تَرَىٰٓ إِذِ ٱلظَّٰلِمُونَ فِى غَمَرَٰتِ ٱلْمَوْتِ وَٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ بَاسِطُوٓا۟ أَيْدِيهِمْ أَخْرِجُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَكُمُ ۖ ٱلْيَوْمَ تُجْزَوْنَ عَذَابَ ٱلْهُونِ بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَقُولُونَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ غَيْرَ ٱلْحَقِّ وَكُنتُمْ عَنْ ءَايَٰتِهِۦ تَسْتَكْبِرُونَ","translation":"And who could be more wicked than he who invents a lie about God, or says, \"This has been revealed unto me,\" the while nothing has been revealed to him? - or he who says, \"I, too, can bestow from on high the like of what God has bestowed\"? If thou couldst but see [how it will be] when these evildoers find themselves in the agonies of death, and the angels stretch forth their hands [and call]: \"Give up your souls! Today you shall be requited with the suffering of humiliation for having attributed to God something that is not true, and for having persistently scorned His messages in your arrogance!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/882.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":69018,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"এবং কে (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_093_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69019,"position":2,"arabic":"أَظْلَمُ","translation":"বড় সীমালঙ্ঘনকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/006_093_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69020,"position":3,"arabic":"مِ